Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:49.82,Pony,,0,0,0,,现在是小马对小马\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NLooks like it's pony vs. pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.32,Pony,,0,0,0,,骏马对骏马\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NSteed vs. steed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:54.23,Pony,,0,0,0,,美女对野兽\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NBeauty vs. beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.19,Pony,,0,0,0,,开玩笑呢 因为我们都是美女\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NAaand kidding, cuz we're all beauties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:00:59.41,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们也是野兽\NAnd we're all beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.71,Pony,,0,0,0,,至少 我觉得不至于\NWell I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.59,Pony,,0,0,0,,真希望我们能在同一支队伍\NI wish we were playing on the same team!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:06.75,Pony,,0,0,0,,这样就能一起赢了\NThat way we'd all win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.50,Pony,,0,0,0,, 或者一起输\NOr all lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.42,Pony,,0,0,0,,只是说有这种可能嘛\NI'm just saying it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:12.68,Pony,,0,0,0,,朋友们也会希望我们全力以赴\NOur friends would want us to give it our all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:15.34,Pony,,0,0,0,,无论输赢，我们都会尽力\NWin or lose, we'll try our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.65,Pony,,0,0,0,,非得分个胜负 让我好纠结\NI'm sad that if we win, they lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.78,Pony,,0,0,0,,反正我不想输\NWell I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:27.70,Pony,,0,0,0,,怎么 你去试镜难道只是为了当个替角?\NWhat?! You don't audition hoping to be the understudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:29.31,Pony,,0,0,0,,她想说的是\NWhat she's tryin' to say is that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.57,Pony,,0,0,0,,哪怕我们要和朋友比赛\Neven though we're competin' against our pals,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.57,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们也要拿出100%的实力\Nwe gotta give it 100 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:36.10,Pony,,0,0,0,,甚至110%\NMaybe 110 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.66,Pony,,0,0,0,,棒 接的好\NYeah nice catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.79,Pony,,0,0,0,,我是说 接的不好?\NI-I mean, bad catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.36,Pony,,0,0,0,,哦 我没办法给她们加油\NOhh! I can't not cheer for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.16,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们加油\NGo us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:20.58,Pony,,0,0,0,,你们加油 \NGo them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.20,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们加油\NGo us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.66,Pony,,0,0,0,,她们加油\NGo them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.07,Pony,,0,0,0,,要是比赛过后她们还是朋友\NIt'll be amazing if these ponies make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.02,Pony,,0,0,0,,那就真是太棒了\Nand are still friends after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:36.77,Pony,,0,0,0,,好了 该回去干活了\NWelp-- gotta get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.31,Pony,,0,0,0,,魔药可不会自己填满柜子\NPotions don't restock themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.52,Pony,,0,0,0,,不会吗?\NThey don't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:43.77,Pony,,0,0,0,,吃灰吧\NEat my dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:47.04,Pony,,0,0,0,,等等 作为专业厨师  我不能让大家吃灰\NWait, as a food professional I can't serve dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:52.49,Pony,,0,0,0,,吃杯糕吧\NEat my cupcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.83,Pony,,0,0,0,,一切都变得清晰起来\NEverything's coming into focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.08,Pony,,0,0,0,,腾空3秒\NThree seconds in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.54,Pony,,0,0,0,,10步一栏\Nten paces per hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:06.67,Pony,,0,0,0,,只要照计算行事 就能赢下赛跑\NThis race can be won using a calculated game plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:10.96,Pony,,0,0,0,,哇 暮暮\NWow, Twi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.63,Pony,,0,0,0,,你重新定义了 "靠头脑比赛"\Nyou give new meaning to getting your head in the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.20,Pony,,0,0,0,,我来给你的比赛添点压力\NI'm giving you a run for your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.24,Pony,,0,0,0,,你是说 "让我很想吃蜂蜜" ?\NYou mean, run for my honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.43,Pony,,0,0,0,,行吧 我不在乎 随便吧\NFine, I don't even care,like whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.44,Pony,,0,0,0,,我在终点线放一罐蜂蜜时 总能跑得更快\NI always run faster when I plant a jar of honey at the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.78,Pony,,0,0,0,,我可没把这点算进去\NI did not calculate for that.
