Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:43.05,Pony,,0,0,0,,将进行的是 长桨比武\Ncompeting in the joust!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.75,Pony,,0,0,0,,获胜队伍将加冕\NThe winning team will be crowned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.23,Pony,,0,0,0,,体育盛宴冠军\NSportacular Spectacular champaculars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.93,Pony,,0,0,0,,她们会因为咱们是朋友就放水吗\NDo you think they'll go easy on us 'cause we're friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.41,Pony,,0,0,0,,她们并没有放慢速度 我们也不能\NThey haven't slowed down yet, so neither will we!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.41,Pony,,0,0,0,,咱们还是得拿出110%的斗志\NLet's still give 110 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.94,Pony,,0,0,0,,也许120%\NMaybe 120 percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.34,Pony,,0,0,0,,不许打我鬃毛\NGentle on the mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.56,Pony,,0,0,0,,哎呀\NYikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.52,Pony,,0,0,0,,太险了\NThat was too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.48,Pony,,0,0,0,,只剩你和我了 伙计\NIt's just you and me, pard'ner.
