Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.76,Pony,,0,0,0,,是是 那当然好啦\NYeah yeah that's great and all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.77,Pony,,0,0,0,,但你至少先说说谁输谁赢\Nbut you gotta tell us who won and who lost
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.77,Pony,,0,0,0,,好让我们回去继续做朋友\Nso we can get back to being friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.99,Pony,,0,0,0,,在不同的队伍不代表你们就不是朋友了\NBeing on different teams doesn't mean you're not friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.65,Pony,,0,0,0,,当你拿出全力比赛\NBy competing your hardest
