Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.49,Pony,,0,0,0,,我都等不及了\NI CAN'T WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:07.58,Pony,,0,0,0,,就不能让我们多睡一会儿吗\NCan't we sleep just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.59,Pony,,0,0,0,,没们儿 小-马\NNo way, po-nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:12.46,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们得早点赶到会场占个好座位\NWe need to get there early or we won't get good seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.85,Pony,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗? 咱们走\NEverypony ready? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:18.42,Pony,,0,0,0,,看吧 全场最棒的座位\NSee? Best seats in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.99,Pony,,0,0,0,,你们怎么睡得着的?\NHow are you ponies asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:25.39,Pony,,0,0,0,,这里充满了活力\NThe energy here is electric!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.83,Pony,,0,0,0,,我的天啊 我们这美容觉睡了多久\NMy hoofness, how long were we beauty-resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.83,Pony,,0,0,0,,也没多久 整个 白天而已 \NOh, not long. Just all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.70,Pony,,0,0,0,,音乐剧马上就开始了\NThe show'll begin any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.96,Pony,,0,0,0,,竞技精神的具现已经到场了\NThere's the Spirit of Competition now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:42.62,Pony,,0,0,0,,太好了 我正找你们呢\NOh good! Just the ponies I was looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.19,Pony,,0,0,0,,我需要你们\NI need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.75,Pony,,0,0,0,,好了 快说说这是怎么回事吧\NNow what in tarnation is goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.72,Pony,,0,0,0,,我这几天深受触动\NI've been so inspired by
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:52.14,Pony,,0,0,0,,因为我见证了你们在体坛盛宴上的表现\Nwatching you compete here at the Sportacular Spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.24,Pony,,0,0,0,,你们不仅是优秀的运动员\NYou are true sportsponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.11,Pony,,0,0,0,,还是更优秀的好朋友\Nbut even better friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:59.42,Pony,,0,0,0,,你们让我领悟到 我也该去做一个好朋友\NYou've shown me that I need to be a better friend too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.46,Pony,,0,0,0,,交朋友可不容易\NBecause friendship can be hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:04.08,Pony,,0,0,0,,但友谊值得为之付出一切\Nbut it's what makes everything worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.95,Pony,,0,0,0,,你说的对\NYou said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.47,Pony,,0,0,0,,所以我想，我为什么要在这里\NSo I thought, why am I here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.26,Pony,,0,0,0,,上演一场完美无缺\Nputting on a perfectly-executed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.87,Pony,,0,0,0,,毕生难遇的演出\Nonce-in-a-lifetime show,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.91,Pony,,0,0,0,,我应去跟我的老朋友兼老对手\Nwhen I should go make things right with my old pal,slash-rival
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.96,Pony,,0,0,0,,浩克•蹄筋  重归于好\NHulk Hamstrings
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.00,Pony,,0,0,0,,我刚才回忆杀了\NI'm having a flashback.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.55,Pony,,0,0,0,,这倒提醒我了 我得把我的绶带  让给你们\NThat reminds me! I-I gotta give my sash back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:23.59,Pony,,0,0,0,,给你小马们\NTo you ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.18,Pony,,0,0,0,,现在你们是竞技精神的实体具现了\NYou're the Spirits of Competition now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.30,Pony,,0,0,0,,等等 大块头先生\NWait, Mr. Biceps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.62,Pony,,0,0,0,,你的演出\NYour show!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.68,Pony,,0,0,0,,不 是你们的演出\NNo, your show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:32.97,Pony,,0,0,0,,你们赢来的\NYou earned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.59,Pony,,0,0,0,,所以...... 闭幕式就交给你们了\NSoooo... you're in charge of the closing ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.41,Pony,,0,0,0,,祝好运\NGood luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.44,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们什么都没有准备\NWe don't have anything prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.28,Pony,,0,0,0,,我们要唱些什么啊\NWhat are we gonna sing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:51.91,FS,,0,0,0,,让我们 歌唱比赛\N♪ A sooong about the games... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.08,FS,,0,0,0,,以及友谊\N♪ And friendshiiip... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:57.30,FS,,0,0,0,,再加上魔法 如果时间够的{\fs50}···{\fs70}话\N♪ And magic if we have tiiiiiiiime ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:59.08,RR,,0,0,0,,我是只出众小马\N♪ I'm a standout pony ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.33,RR,,0,0,0,,永远的赢家\N♪ a winner through and through ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.87,RR,,0,0,0,,但生活这出戏码\N♪ But I'm just a one mare show ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.55,RR,,0,0,0,,不能少了你和她\N♪ Without you and you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:05.22,Chorus,,0,0,0,,还有你\NAnd you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:06.34,RR,,0,0,0,,没有朋友\N♪ Without friends ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.79,RR,,0,0,0,,华美也只流于苍白\N♪ I'm a lime without the light ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.47,RR,,0,0,0,,当我们凝成一团\N♪ When we are together... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:13.01,PP,,0,0,0,,更闪耀着光彩\N♪ We shine extra bright! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.72,Chorus,,0,0,0,,友谊并不简单\N♪ It isn't always easy ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.32,Chorus,,0,0,0,,相处也会是考验\N♪ Friendship can be hard ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.37,Chorus,,0,0,0,,珍视每个伙伴\N♪ But for every friend I have ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.85,Chorus,,0,0,0,,用心维系浇灌\N♪ I'd trot that extra yard ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.31,Chorus,,0,0,0,,我永远支持你\N♪ I've always got your back ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.11,Chorus,,0,0,0,,奔向梦中目的地\N♪ For any goal you dream ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:26.16,Chorus,,0,0,0,,无论相聚或分离\N♪ Together or apart ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.33,Chorus,,0,0,0,,我们心都在一起\N♪ We make the perfect team! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.00,AJ,,0,0,0,,遭遇瓶颈难闯过\N♪ If you hit an obstacle ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:32.25,AJ,,0,0,0,,我帮你找回执着\N♪ I'll help ya stay on course ♪
